data.description: New year, your new home! Built for elegance and comfort, the layout of  this two-story classic home boats over 2000 sq ft of living space. Large foyer with double door entry creates a welcoming first impression. Large bonus living space opens to a formal dining room, perfect for hosting special occasions. The kitchen is the heart of this home, with an abundance of cabinets & countertop space, a full pantry, & a breakfast island that seamlessly connects to an open living room with fireplace. Double doors from the living room lead to a covered screened porch, making it easy to transition from indoor to outdoor living. Upstairs, discover spacious bedrooms including the master bedroom with walk-in closet & ensuite bathroom. Attached two-car garage. Situated on an oversized corner lot, the beautifully landscaped yard is enhanced by a wood fence, creating a nearly private and aesthetically pleasing outdoor space. Opportunity for the new owners to personalize and make this house their own.
